name: NSKeyedUnarchiverDelegate
desc: The optional methods implemented by the delegate of a keyed unarchiver.

items.name: func unarchiver(NSKeyedUnarchiver, cannotDecodeObjectOfClassName: String, originalClasses: [String]) -> AnyClass?
items.desc: Informs the delegate that the class with a given name is not available during decoding.

items.name: func unarchiver(NSKeyedUnarchiver, didDecode: Any?) -> Any?
items.desc: Informs the delegate that a given object has been decoded.

items.name: func unarchiver(NSKeyedUnarchiver, willReplace: Any, with: Any)
items.desc: Informs the delegate that one object is being substituted for another.

items.name: func unarchiverDidFinish(NSKeyedUnarchiver)
items.desc: Notifies the delegate that decoding has finished.

items.name: func unarchiverWillFinish(NSKeyedUnarchiver)
items.desc: Notifies the delegate that decoding is about to finish.
